/*
Data required in the 2023 Q2 PT's Inventory Prop Forecast file

Based on Mansie's code for 2022 Q4 https://zeta.dss.vip.ebay.com/zeta/share/#/notebook?notebookId=cf596504-353e-4924-bcca-1e671f660107
(completely separate from verticals' inventory props, PT get their own forecast (no need to split out Core forecast with PT)
